<commentary>atha samāhitāntaḥkaraṇaḥ sankiṃ kṛtavānityata āha-pratyāsanna iti || sa yakṣaḥ | yaś ciraṃ dadhyau sa ity arthaḥ | nabhasi śrāvaṇe  "namaḥ khaṃ śrāvaṇo nabhāḥ" ity amaraḥ || pratyāsanne āṣāḍhasyānantaraṃ sannikṛṣṭe | prāpte satīty arthaḥ | dayitājīvitālambanārthī san | varṣākālasya virahaduḥkhajanakatvāt "utpannānarthapratīkārād anarthotpattipratibandha eva varam" iti nyāyena prāg eva priyāprāṇadhāraṇopāyaṃ cikīrṣur ity arthaḥ | jīvanasyodakasya mūtaḥ paṭabandho vastrabandho jīmūtaḥ || pṛṣodarāditvāt sādhuḥ | "mūtaḥ syāt paṭabandhe 'pi" iti rudraḥ || tena jīmūtena jaladhareṇa prayojyena svakuśalamayīṃ svakṣemapradhānāṃ pravṛttiṃ vārtām || "vārtā pravṛttir vṛttāntaḥ" ity amaraḥ || hārayiṣyan prāpayiṣyan | "ḷṭ śeṣe ca" iti cakārāt kriyārthakriyopapadāl ḷṛṭpratyayaḥ | jīvanārthaṃ karma jīvanapradenaiva kartavyam iti bhāvaḥ || "hṛkror anyatarasyām" iti karmasaṃjñāyā vikalpāt pakṣe kartari tṛtīyā || pratyagrair abhinavaiḥ kuṭajakusumair girimallikābhiḥ || "kuṭajo girimallikā" iti halāyudhaḥ || kalpitārghāya kalpito 'nuṣṭhitaḥ pūjāvidhir yasmai tasmai || "mūlye pūjāvidhāv arghaḥ" ity amaraḥ || tasmai jīmūtāya || "kriyāgrahaṇam api kartavyam" iti sampradānatvāc caturthī || prītipramukhāni prītipūrvakāṇi vacanāni yasmin karmaṇi tat prītipramukhavacanaṃ yathā tathā | śobhanam āgataṃ svāgataṃ svāgatavacanaṃ prītaḥ sanvyājahāra | kuśalāgamanaṃ papracchety arthaḥ || nāthena tv atra "pratyāsanne manasi" iti sādhīyān pāṭhaḥ kalpitaḥ | pratyāsanne prakṛtimāpanne satīty arthaḥ | yas tu tenaiva pūrvapāṭhavirodhaḥ pradarśitaḥ so 'smābhiḥ "āṣāḍhasya prathamadivase" ity etatpāṭhavikalpa samādhānenaiva samādhāya parihṛtaḥ ||</commentary>

nanu cetana sādhyam arthaṃ katham acetanena kārayituṃ pravṛtta ity apekṣāyāṃ kaviḥ samādhatte—dhūmeti |